.\" Man page for simple_shell
.\" See man(7) for more information.
TH simple_shell "1" "December 2023" "Holberton School"

.SH NAME
simple_shell \- a simple shell command interpreter

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B simple_shell

.SH DESCRIPTION
.B simple_shell
is a command-line interpreter that allows users to execute commands.

.SH COMPILATION
Compile the shell using the following command:
.PP
.EX
gcc -Wall -Werror -Wextra -pedantic -std=gnu89 *.c -o hsh
.EE

.SH USAGE
Run the shell by executing the compiled binary:
.PP
.EX
./hsh
.EE

.SH EXAMPLES
.EX
$ ls
file1  file2  file3
$ pwd
/path/to/current/directory
.EE

.SH AUTHORS
.B Matio Bouchot
